<% layout('layouts/boilerplate') %>

<div class="container mt-5 mb-5">
    <h1 class="text-center mb-4">Creator Resources</h1>
    <p class="text-center text-muted" style="width: 60%; margin: 0 auto">
        If you've ever dreamed of bringing a creative idea to life and sharing
        it with a supportive community, you've found the perfect place.
    </p>
    <hr
        style="width: 80%; height: 4px; background-color: black; border: none"
        class="mx-auto mt-5"
    />

    <!-- Getting Started Section -->
    <section class="my-5">
        <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
                <img
                    src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1506748686214-e9df14d4d9d0?w=800&auto=format&fit=crop&q=60"
                    alt="Getting Started"
                    class="img-fluid rounded shadow-sm"
                />
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-8">
                <h2 class="mb-4">Getting Started with Your Project</h2>
                <p>
                    Your project is a reflection of your vision and creativity.
                    It can be anything you aspire to create and share, as long
                    as it has a clear goal and outcome. To set you on the right
                    path, every Boomerang project should include:
                </p>
                <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-success"></i> A
                        compelling project page with a video and description
                        that tells your story.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-success"></i>
                        Rewards for backers who support your project.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-success"></i>
                        Updates that keep backers engaged as your project
                        progresses.
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <p class="mt-3">
                    Let's delve into each of these elements to help you build a
                    successful campaign.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Crafting Your Project Page Section -->
    <section class="mb-5">
        <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div
                style="
                    width: 450px; /* Set a fixed width */
                    border-top: 3px solid #007bff;
                    margin-bottom: 1rem;
                "
            ></div>
            <div class="col-md-8">
                <h2 class="pt-5 mb-4">Crafting Your Project Page</h2>
                <p>
                    Think of your project page as a conversation with a friend.
                    How would you describe your idea? What questions might they
                    ask? This is your opportunity to share who you are, what
                    you're creating, and why it matters.
                </p>
                <p>Here are some key questions to address:</p>
                <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        <strong>Who Are You?</strong> Introduce yourself and
                        your team. Share your background, experiences, and any
                        previous work that highlights your capabilities.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        <strong>What Are You Creating?</strong> Provide detailed
                        information about your project. Include sketches,
                        prototypes, or samples to give backers a clear
                        understanding of your vision.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        <strong>Why This Project?</strong> Explain the
                        inspiration behind your idea. Sharing the story of how
                        your project came to be helps others connect with your
                        passion.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        <strong>What's Your Plan and Schedule?</strong> Outline
                        a realistic timeline. Let backers know what to expect
                        and when.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        <strong>How Will You Use the Funds?</strong> Offer a
                        simple budget breakdown. Transparency builds trust and
                        assures backers that you have a solid plan.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        <strong>Why Does It Matter to You?</strong> Express your
                        enthusiasm and commitment. Your passion can inspire
                        others to join you on your journey.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
                <img
                    src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1595280494555-73052c13ee0e?w=800&auto=format&fit=crop&q=60&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHx0b3BpYy1mZWVkfDM1fEZ6bzN6dU9ITjZ3fHxlbnwwfHx8fHw%3D"
                    alt="Crafting Page"
                    class="img-fluid rounded shadow-sm"
                />
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Enhancing Your Story Section -->
    <section class="mb-5">
        <div
            style="
                width: 500px; /* Set a fixed width */
                border-top: 3px solid #007bff;
                margin-left: auto; /* Align to the right */
                margin-bottom: 1rem;
            "
        ></div>
        <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
                <img
                    src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1527474305487-b87b222841cc?w=800&auto=format&fit=crop&q=60"
                    alt="Enhance Story"
                    class="img-fluid rounded shadow-sm"
                />
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-8 text-end">
                <h2 class="pt-5 mb-4">Enhancing Your Story with Media</h2>
                <p>
                    While words are powerful, incorporating visuals and media
                    can bring your project to life. Here are some tips:
                </p>
                <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        <strong>Choose an Eye-Catching Project Image:</strong>
                        This is the first impression of your project—make it
                        count.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        <strong>Create an Engaging Video:</strong> Introduce
                        yourself and your project personally. Authenticity
                        resonates more than high production value.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        <strong>Include Captions and Subtitles:</strong> Make
                        your content accessible to a wider audience.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        <strong>Use Creative Elements:</strong> Integrate
                        images, gifs, or sound clips to enrich your story.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Designing Rewards Section -->
    <section class="mb-5">
        <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div
                style="
                    width: 450px; /* Set a fixed width */
                    border-top: 3px solid #007bff;
                    margin-bottom: 1rem;
                "
            ></div>
            <div class="col-md-8">
                <h2 class="pt-5 mb-4">Designing Rewards for Backers</h2>
                <p>
                    Backers support projects they believe in, but offering
                    meaningful rewards enhances their experience. Consider the
                    following:
                </p>
                <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        <strong>What to Offer:</strong> Rewards directly related
                        to your project—digital downloads, physical products, or
                        exclusive experiences.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        <strong>How to Price Rewards:</strong> Set fair pledge
                        amounts with options ranging from modest to premium.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        <strong>Limit Reward Tiers:</strong> Keep tiers
                        manageable, especially for your first project. We
                        recommend up to five tiers.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        <strong>Set Clear Delivery Expectations:</strong>
                        Provide realistic estimated delivery dates for each
                        reward.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
                <img
                    src="https://plus.unsplash.com/premium_photo-1690522330770-85a5ad8cee3b?w=800&auto=format&fit=crop&q=60&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHx0b3BpYy1mZWVkfDM0fEZ6bzN6dU9ITjZ3fHxlbnwwfHx8fHw%3D"
                    alt="Designing Rewards"
                    class="img-fluid rounded shadow-sm"
                />
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Setting your funding goal -->
    <section class="mb-5">
        <div
            style="
                width: 500px; /* Set a fixed width */
                border-top: 3px solid #007bff;
                margin-left: auto; /* Align to the right */
                margin-bottom: 1rem;
            "
        ></div>
        <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
                <img
                    src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1527474305487-b87b222841cc?w=800&auto=format&fit=crop&q=60"
                    alt="Enhance Story"
                    class="img-fluid rounded shadow-sm"
                />
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-8 text-end">
                <h2 class="pt-5 mb-4">Setting Your Funding Goal</h2>
                <p>
                    Boomerang operates on an all-or-nothing funding model. This
                    means you should set a funding goal that covers all the
                    expenses necessary to complete your project and fulfill
                    rewards.
                </p>
                <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        <strong>List All Expenses:</strong> Include production
                        costs, materials, fees, and a buffer for unforeseen
                        costs. Consider Your Audience Reach: Estimate how many
                        backers you can realistically attract.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        <strong>Include Platform Fees:</strong> Estimate how
                        many backers you can realistically attract. Include
                        Platform Fees: Remember to factor in Boomerang's 5% fee
                        and payment processing fees.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        <strong>Set a Realistic Timeline: </strong> Campaigns
                        can run from 1 to 90 days, but shorter durations can
                        create a sense of urgency.
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        <strong>Utilizing Boomerang's Tools: </strong> We
                        provide various tools to help you manage and promote
                        your project.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Final Thoughts Section -->
    <section class="mb-5">
        <h2 class="mb-4">Final Thoughts</h2>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <p class="lead">
                    Embarking on a creative project is an exciting venture, and
                    we're here to support you every step of the way. By
                    carefully planning, engaging with your community, and
                    staying true to your vision, you can successfully launch
                    your idea into reality.
                </p>
                <p class="text-center mt-4">
                    <a href="/rules" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-lg"
                        >Visit Project Guidelines</a
                    >
                    <a href="/projects/new" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg ml-3"
                        >Get Started Now</a
                    >
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>
